[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **FUNCTION CALL ALTERNATIVES:**                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```javascript                                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m alert(1)                      → alert`1`                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → alert.call(null,1)                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → alert.apply(null,[1])                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → Reflect.apply(alert,null,[1])                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → [1].map(alert)                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → [1].find(alert)                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → [1].filter(alert)                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → [1].forEach(alert)                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → [1].every(alert)                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → [1].findIndex(alert)                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **BYPASS PARENTHESIS:**                                                      [34m│[0m
