[34m│[0m ### Event Handler Enumeration                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **ALWAYS-FIRE EVENTS (no user interaction):**                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `onload` (img, body, iframe, svg, script, link, style)                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `onerror` (img, script, link, audio, video)                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `onanimationend` (any element with CSS animation)                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `onfocus` + `autofocus` (input, textarea, select, a, button)               [34m│[0m
