[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **USER-INTERACTION EVENTS (backup):**                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `onclick`, `ondblclick`                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `onmouseover`, `onmouseenter`                                              [34m│[0m
